      <title>TRM 表示，Tether 是非法加密货币流通中最常用的稳定币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/tether-usdt-is-most-used-stablecoin-in-illicit-crypto-flows-trm-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[TRM Labs 的数据显示，去年，Tether 是加密货币犯罪活动中最常用的稳定币，随着越来越多的数字资产机构面临制裁，该行业的非法交易总量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/tether-usdt-is-most-used-stablecoin-in-illicit-crypto-flows-trm-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
